We used to play a lot when we were kids.

49
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:09,020
And if you call it a fire, it's this.

50
00:03:09,480 --> 00:03:10,520
Cha-cha-cha!

51
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:12,980
It's the King of Fire, Fireworks!

52
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:14,480
What?

53
00:03:14,580 --> 00:03:15,720
What a size!

54
00:03:16,100 --> 00:03:17,060
It's no good, Ryo!

55
00:03:17,060 --> 00:03:19,140
That's right, in a place like this...

56
00:03:19,140 --> 00:03:20,380
What are you talking about?

57
00:03:21,300 --> 00:03:23,000
The firework is what makes the sky so bright.

58
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:28,420
I made this for you.

59
00:03:28,620 --> 00:03:29,940
It's the 200th time I've made it.

60
00:03:29,940 --> 00:03:30,480
What?

61
00:03:30,720 --> 00:03:31,680
Get out of the way!

62
00:03:35,620 --> 00:03:43,420
It won't come up.

63
00:03:44,060 --> 00:03:45,660
That's strange.

64
00:03:49,160 --> 00:03:49,800
It's the plan of the great king.

65
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:51,080
Ohara-kun, it seems there's no one.

66
00:03:52,320 --> 00:03:53,620
That's not right.

67
